---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<style>
  .heading {
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-decoration-color: #cccccc;
    text-decoration-thickness: 2px;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }

  .bio-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding-left: 0;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  img {
    border-radius: 100%;
    width: 300px;
    height: 350px;
  }

  .flavor-section {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-rows: 400px auto;
    row-gap: 50px;
    justify-items: center;
  }

  @media (min-width: 600px) {
    .flavor-section {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 300px auto;
      column-gap: 50px;
      align-items: center;
    }
  }
</style>
<BaseLayout title="Home" name="Brennan Manning">
  <div class = "flavor-section">
      <img src="assets/cropped-portrait.jpeg" alt="Headshot"/>
      <p>
        Hi there. I'm Brennan Manning, a recent graduate from the
        University of Amsterdam where I got my Masters' in Econometrics with a
        specialization in Financial Econometrics. Right now I'm interested in option pricing
        and I'm currently writing a python library to help with this. Outside of that, some of my hobbies are
        reading, programming, and learning. Right now, some of my projects are building this website
        and customizing an old PC to test out Void Linux. I am also attempting to read Ulysses by James
        Joyce again. 
      </p>
  </div>

  <h3 class="heading">Bio</h3>
  <ul class="bio-list">
    <li>
      <b>1998</b>: Born in Baltimore, MD
    </li>
    <li>
      <b>2017</b>: Moved to Amsterdam, NL
    </li>
    <li>
      <b>2020</b>: Finished BSc. program in Econometrics
    </li>
    <li>
      <b>2021</b>: Finished MSc. program in Econometrics
    </li>
  </ul>
</BaseLayout>
